OL,3,CCalls for kettle prison ban after
OL,4,CSouthport killer alleged attack
OL,6,FThe shadow justice secretary also
OL,7,Fcalled for the removal of kettles from
OL,8,Fall high-risk prisoners, after
OL,9,FSouthport killer Axel Rudakubana
OL,10,Fallegedly poured boiling water over an
OL,11,Fofficer.
OL,13,FA prison officer will be killed if the
OL,14,FGovernment does not "get a grip" of
OL,15,F"spiralling" violence by prisoners,
OL,16,FRobert Jenrick has warned.
OL,18,F18-year-old Rudakubana allegedly used
OL,19,Fa kettle in his cell to heat the water
OL,20,Fbefore the attack at HMP Belmarsh on
OL,21,FThursday 8 May.
