OL,3,CCalls for kettle prison ban after
OL,4,CSouthport killer alleged attack
OL,6,FIt comes after four guards were
OL,7,Fattacked with hot oil and homemade
OL,8,Fweapons by Manchester Arena bomb
OL,9,Fplotter Hashem Abedi at HMP Frankland
OL,10,Fin April.
OL,12,FJustice minister Sir Nicholas Dakin
OL,13,Fsaid the Government will do "whatever
OL,14,Fis takes" to ensure the safety of
OL,15,Fthose working in prisons and is
OL,16,Ftrusting the expertise of prison staff.
OL,18,FIn an urgent question, Mr Jenrick told
OL,19,Fthe Commons: "Violence against
OL,20,Fofficers has spiralled out of control.
OL,26,@uD@]OUvD@IO]{D@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
