OL,3,CCalls for kettle prison ban after
OL,4,CSouthport killer alleged attack
OL,6,F"In just the past month, two of
OL,7,FBritain's most dangerous terrorists,
OL,8,FAxel Rudakubana and Hashem Abedi, have
OL,9,Flaunched vicious attacks on officers
OL,10,Fin two of our supposedly most secure
OL,11,Fprisons."
OL,13,FMr Jenrick continued: "The Secretary
OL,14,Fof State has ordered a snap review
OL,15,Finto the attack at HMP Frankland `
OL,16,Fthree weeks later, no answers and no
OL,17,Faction. Every day longer it goes on,
OL,18,Fthe safety of officers is at risk.
OL,26,@uD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
