OL,3,CCalls for kettle prison ban after
OL,4,CSouthport killer alleged attack
OL,6,F"I couldn't care less if Rudakubana
OL,7,Fnever had a hot drink again, nor would
OL,8,Fthe British public. This culture of
OL,9,Fappeasement, of protecting the rights
OL,10,Fof convicted terrorists and criminals
OL,11,Fover the safety of our officers must
OL,12,Fend, and it must end now.
OL,14,F"If that means keeping them in cells
OL,15,Fwith just a bed, so be it. If it means
OL,16,Fno contact, no privileges and
OL,17,Fcertainly no cups of tea, so be it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
