OL,3,CCalls for kettle prison ban after
OL,4,CSouthport killer alleged attack
OL,6,F"Let segregation truly and finally
OL,7,Fmean segregation, because ` and I want
OL,8,Fto say this as clearly as I can ` I am
OL,9,Fwarning the House now, if the
OL,10,FGovernment does not get a grip, a
OL,11,Fprison officer will be killed. We've
OL,12,Fhad enough reviews, we need action.
OL,13,FThat's the least prison officers
OL,14,Fdeserve."
OL,16,FSir Nicholas had earlier told the
OL,17,FCommons the Government is committed to
OL,18,Fmaking sure those who work in the UK's
OL,19,Fprisons are safe and updates on the
OL,20,Fincident at HMP Belmarsh will be
OL,21,Fprovided "in due course".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]}D@JOU}D@XO]
