OL,6,FHe also said an update on the
OL,7,Findependent review into the incident
OL,8,Fat HMP Frankland will be given "in the
OL,9,Fcoming days".
OL,11,FResponding to Mr Jenrick, he said: "We
OL,12,Fare managing the most complex people
OL,13,Fin the most complex system. Our prison
OL,14,Fstaff have to manage extremely
OL,15,Fdangerous people, and they do it with
OL,16,Freal bravery, and we will do whatever
OL,17,Fit takes to keep them safe, and that
OL,18,Fis why we have taken the actions we
OL,19,Falready have.
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@LO]sD@dOU
