OL,6,FSome 10,605 assaults on staff in male
OL,7,Fand female jails were recorded in
OL,8,F2024, up from 9,204 in 2023 and nearly
OL,9,Fthree times the 3,640 in 2014.
OL,11,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,12,Fpreviously announced that the use of
OL,13,Ftasers will be trialled in prisons and
OL,14,Fconfirmed the Prison Service will
OL,15,Fconduct a "snap review" of the use of
OL,16,Fprotective body armour for prison
OL,17,Fofficers.
