OL,6,FLabour MP Luke Akehurst said he had
OL,7,Fheard "activist lawyers and the courts
OL,8,Fthat are insisting that these
OL,9,Fdangerous terrorist prisoners have
OL,10,Faccess to kettles and the ability to
OL,11,Fuse kitchens".
OL,13,FThe North Durham MP added: "Will the
OL,14,FGovernment consider changes to primary
OL,15,Flegislation to enable these privileges
OL,16,Fto be removed from that category of
OL,17,Fprisoners?"
OL,19,FSir Nicholas said "access to kitchens
OL,20,Fhas immediately been withdrawn" after
OL,21,Frecent incidents.
