OL,6,FConservative former minister and
OL,7,FTatton MP Esther McVey suggested that
OL,8,Fviolent prisoners should "forfeit any
OL,9,Fright" to privileges.
OL,11,FShe said: "Surely as a minimum, any
OL,12,Fprisoner who assaults a prison officer
OL,13,Fshould automatically forfeit any right
OL,14,Fto early release and all privileges.
OL,16,F"Does the minister agree and if so,
OL,17,Fwhen will he introduce that change,
OL,18,Fand if not, why not?"
